            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Monster Core pg. 103",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 103,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "While many know orcas as \u201ckiller whales,\u201d they're actually the largest species of dolphin. These powerful animals hunt together in pods to take down seals, sharks, and even whales. Adult orcas are typically 15\u201325 feet long and weigh 8,000\u201312,000 pounds.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
